Feature: Avis

    This charm creates a flock of birds from the caster's wand. When coupled
    with Oppugno, it can be used offensively.

    Pronunciation:
        /ˈeɪvɨs/ AY-vis
    Seen/mentioned:
        Shown in Goblet of Fire, cast by Mr Ollivander to test Viktor Krum's
        wand.[GF Ch.18] In Half-Blood Prince, it is cast by Hermione, followed
        by Oppugno which causes the birds to attack Ron.[HBP Ch.14]
